MAN 
manual pages provide various info realted to commands 

# man man : to see the manual page of the man command

# man [ command ] : to see the man page of specific command

press q : to quit from the man page

press h : to view the additonal info related to man page

# man [ section number ]    [ command ] : to see the specific section of the man page

/[keyword] : to search for any keyword inside the man page

n : to move from top to bottom through the matches found

N : to move from bottom to top through the matches found

g or < : to navigate to the starting of the man page

G or > : to navigate to the ending of the man page 

# mandb : to update all the indexes of man db

